Class RandomKeySet

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeySource<ByteArrayKey>

    public class RandomKeySet
extends KeySet<ByteArrayKey>
    A source of pre-generated keys filled with pseudo-random numbers. This class uses RandomKeyStream during construction to create the keys.
    Author:
    David Curtis
